        "هِ اَلتِّبْنُ يُطَيَّنُ بِهِ اَلْمَسْجِدُ أَوِ اَلْبَيْتُ اَلَّذِي يُصَلَّى فِيهِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.709 - Abu Al-Hasan al-Awwal, Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as), was asked about using clay mixed with straw to plaster the mosque or the house where prayers are offered.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
        ]
